---
title: Reckoning the Dead
layout: layouts/base
section: "reckoning-the-dead"
---

<section class="max-w-content mx-auto px-6 py-16 md:py-24 space-y-12">

  <header class="space-y-4">
    <h1 class="font-serif text-display text-ink">Reckoning the Dead</h1>
    <p class="text-lead text-ink-secondary max-w-xl">
      Unearthing the greats who got lost in time.
    </p>
  </header>

  <div class="prose-site text-ink-secondary">
    <p>
      On a rather sunny day, I was commuting to work on Bus 30 to Nuremberg. We had
      just passed the Flughafen while I was reading about the brilliance of Henri
      Poincaré in <em>Antifragile</em>. I was awestruck — the guy understood chaos
      theory and relativity before they were even things. How did I not know about
      him until now?
    </p>
    <p>
      Thinking back, I realized I've always been drawn to exploring forgotten
      ideas and people. Why not log and share it? Why not make it public so more
      people can enjoy these underrated gems?
    </p>
    <p>
      I am a polymath, so you might find my exploration biased, but that's what
      attracts me most. Aim is to explore the lives and ideas of the greats who
      are either forgotten or remain unknown outside their narrow fields of work.
      I want to understand how they approached everything, from everyday problems
      to the big questions.
    </p>
    <p>
      We will never know the works that have long since turned to smoke, but
      let's make the best of whatever is left. Join me as I dig through
      history's footnotes to find the people and thoughts that deserve a second look.
    </p>
  </div>

  <ol class="index-list list-none m-0 p-0">
    {% for post in collections.reckoningTheDead %}
      <li>
        <a href="{{ post.url }}" class="index-row">
          <h2 class="index-row__title">{{ post.data.title | smartTitleCase }}</h2>
          {% if post.data.description %}
            <p class="index-row__desc">{{ post.data.description }}</p>
          {% endif %}
        </a>
      </li>
    {% endfor %}
  </ol>

</section>
